---
description: Keep test payloads in fixtures
globs:
  - "**/*Test.kt"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Do not inline multiline JSON payloads directly inside tests.
- Add payload builders/samples in `*Fixtures.kt` and reference them from tests.
- If a test needs a new payload variant, extend the existing fixture object instead of duplicating JSON.
- Keep fixture values deterministic by default; only use runtime-random values when the test is specifically about that behavior.
